      "body" : "Java will optimize away the object allocation if your loop is hot. See <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/vm/performance-enhancements-7.html#escapeAnalysis\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/vm/&hellip;</a>"
    } ],
