    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>(KOTLIN) For Difference between a constant date and current date (Joda)</strong></p>\n<p>You can use <code>Days.daysBetween(jodaDate1,jodaDate2)</code></p>\n<p>Here is an example:</p>\n<pre><code>        val dateTime: DateTime = DateTime.parse(&quot;14/09/2020&quot;,\n            DateTimeFormat.forPattern(&quot;dd/MM/yyyy&quot;))\n        val currentDate = DateTime.now()\n        //To calculate the days in between\n        val dayCount = Days.daysBetween(dateTime,currentDate).days\n        //Set Value to TextView \n        binding.daysCount.text = dayCount.toString()\n</code></pre>\n"
